milestones.description: Steve Tikolo has become the top scorer for KENYA in ODIs with 688 runs, going past Otieno's 624
Steve Tikolo and Odumbe's 131-run partnership is KENYA's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 118 between Steve Tikolo and Odumbe
Aasif Karim has broken the record for most ducks (4) in ODIs for KENYA, going past Martin Suji's 3
Aasif Karim has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (23) for KENYA, going past Hitesh Modi
This is the highest match aggregate (496) involving teams Zimbabwe & Kenya in ODIs
